snippet.title: CryptoFights presents: Robyn Hood 🏹💚
snippet.description:
Fyx Gaming has partnered with Zenescope & Epik.GG to release Robyn Hood on the Fyx NFT Marketplace 🏹💚

This NFT includes The Dark One + an exclusive digital comic book download!
Get your limited edition CryptoFights skin before it's gone! There are only 500 available and once they're sold, they're gone forever~

👇 Link to purchase on Fyx:
https://fyx.live/robynhood

👇 Zenescope Official:
https://www.youtube.com/c/zenescopeentertainment

👇 Epik GG:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6oC_SNYkMMTQO4InoSY3Ag
